      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "COOL BLUE YOU (1) settled back off the inside but went through her gears strongly to find the frame with a 1.3 lengths third (31.11) at this track in Grade 6. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings three times from three starts. Deserves serious consideration. ICE COOL BLUE (4) jumped from the inside and boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten one length (31.10) behind Adhana Patrick at this track. Has a strong record from this draw, notching three wins and three minor placings from six starts. Racing well and deserves a win. KICKER DUSTY (2) placed three back at this track then out of the placings last couple but moves to box 2 this time where he has performed well. Has the ability and can find best this time. WEBLEC SHIRALEE (6) placed last time out at big odds - worth considering.",
